Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}現在的你 全力支持著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在的我 也有了支持你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使彷徨無助 我們也要結伴前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}奔向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與朋友們嬉戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}這樣一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻依然感到內心的空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受盡冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}寄身於時代的狂風中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}勇氣與不安 如影相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}因此 現在就要用我的雙手創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}那些讓我們受傷感到絕望的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些令我們哭泣感到難過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然縈繞於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們終將跨過重重障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}以超越所有人為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}君が今僕を支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が今君を支える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから迷いながらも共に生きていこうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲間と戯れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}それなりで居ても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もの足りなさを感じてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷めた目で見られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}乾いた時代の風に吹かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}不安な心と勇気が背中合わせになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}だけど今なら夢をこの手で叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}傷ついて壊れそうな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙して困らせる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕達はそれを越えていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}誰より上を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:49.06,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經幻想 夢中的幸福{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:56.02,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人親手為我實現{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:03.08,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在繁忙的都市中尋找藉口{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:09.83,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們都在編織著美麗的謊言{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:17.39,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你這樣 真的滿足了嗎?」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:25.54,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在內心深處審視自己{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.26,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒能與你相遇{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.63,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會強顏歡笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.70,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著虛偽的面具度過{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.45,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你眼中的堅定{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.67,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我逐漸改變{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.53,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了擺脫昨日飄浮不定的心緒…{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:49.06,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に見ていたシアワセなら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:56.02,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが運んでくれると思ってた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:03.08,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急ぎ足の街で言い訳ばかり{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:09.83,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなも同じとうそぶいてた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:17.39,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「本当にキミはいま　満足してるの？」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:25.54,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の真ん中見抜かれたようで{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.26,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたと出会えなかったら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.63,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽った笑顔のまま{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.70,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うわべの態度や言葉を繰り返したね{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.45,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの瞳の力で{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.67,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私は変わってゆこう{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.53,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日の揺らいた気持ちを脱ぎ捨てるために…{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【註釋】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 NCC杯快棋賽就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.98,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「NCC杯快棋賽」：原型為「NEC杯快棋賽」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 國際業餘圍棋大賽我被選定為美國代表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:31.83,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「國際業餘圍棋大賽」：原型為「世界業餘圍棋錦標賽」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,s—a—i
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:47.43,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai是日文「佐為」的羅馬音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已經學會「征子」和「枷」的下法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.87,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「枷」：一種提子方法 不直接打吃而是從遠處包圍對方棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安時代的棋師 藤原佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越了遙遠的時空 在進藤光的心中復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了領悟「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至讓我以為看到了「神之一手」…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\pos(362,384)}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\pos(362,375)}隱藏在網上的棋士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣下怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是只把這邊連起來比較好?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果他在這裏叫吃的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說小亮老師要參加職業考試?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天早上從室井先生那裏聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎? 市河小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是大新聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年的圍棋界可就熱鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為他今年肯定是不想參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮老師發生了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 我問他最近學校的圍棋社怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是小亮什麼也沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只說「那個已經不重要了 只是去玩玩而已」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我也來杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:03:00.70,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(222,413,172,447)\bord0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}{\fs19}第14屆 NCC杯快棋賽 第5局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:05.45,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(480,137,729,137)\bord0}{\c&HA9A27B&}{\fs20}第14屆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:05.45,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(480,199,729,199)\bord0}{\c&H685650&}{\fs20}NCC杯快棋賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:05.45,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(480,241,729,241)\bord0}{\c&HA9A27B&}{\fs17}第1回合 第5局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您現在訂閱一年我們的雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將會為您打折
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也可以在網上下圍棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來試試看怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.51,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,409)\bord0}{\c&H000000&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\fr18}{\fs19}NCC杯快棋賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 二十九 就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是離這麼遠看比賽有意思嗎? 筒井學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業棋手會使用大型棋盤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且會一步一步講解給我們聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是旁邊的人這麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下棋的人不會覺得很煩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(368,22,65,22)\bord0}{\c&HA9A27B&}{\fr1}{\fs19}第14屆NCC杯快棋賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣才開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大的棋盤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 佐為好像也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場的觀眾們 電視機前的觀眾們 大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十四屆NCC杯快棋賽第一回合第五局比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將在藤澤喜久夫九段和高田光一七段之間展開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村瀨九段將為大家做講解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉永二段將為大家記錄棋步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就馬上進入比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 村瀨九段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為今天比賽的焦點將是什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}藤澤九段在名人戰循環賽以及本因坊戰循環賽中的成績…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起佐為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和塔矢的對局結果是我下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{fad(0,200)}塔矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不親自嘗試是無法知道答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己和這傢伙之間的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡鬧了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對不起塔矢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明那麼想和佐為對局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白他的用意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 接下來他會下到這裏吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十五秒  六、七、八…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4·十二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老師 您說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是站在這裏瞎說 薪水可不是白拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過以後該怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也想讓佐為偶爾下下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那傢伙實在太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好我就成了靠運氣獲勝的棋王了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的形勢非常嚴峻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}十秒  一、二、三、四…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4·十三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 下在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 完全沒注意看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個子被提掉了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過他可能會從這裏叫吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來試著擺一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下的話 這裏 這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要看下去嗎? 筒井學長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要看下去 因為比賽還沒結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去大廳裏轉轉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一動不動地坐在那裏看 我實在是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直盼著今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這裏有賣圍棋書的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊好像也有人用電腦在下圍棋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佐為 我們去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是和你爸爸一起來的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 和朋友一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很少見啊 你家裏有電腦嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你對網絡方面感興趣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在這個孩子就是在網上下圍棋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他執黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 剛才他的對手下了一個白子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來又到這孩子的黑子下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 下那裏的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊? 這可不是電視遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得馬上道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 不好意思 突然中斷了比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你這傢伙! 吃你幾個子你就不玩了啊!」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「白癡!!」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先被他罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也應該是個小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是小孩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是他的說話方式和使用的用戶名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得他很像個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用戶名?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上網時用的假名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,zelda啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在網上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會顯示出你的相貌、年齡和真實姓名的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也不能完全肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是小孩 你看 還有外國人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JPN代表日本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHN代表中國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CAN代表加拿大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有USA和GER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那NLD呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是荷蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個列表上的人可以邀請別人對局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以被別人邀請對局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用步驟和操作方法都很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 想找人一起對局的時候就點這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再點這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想試試看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了 還是先教我更詳細的操作方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要登錄吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就從進入這個首頁開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先這樣 進入世界圍棋網 然後進行搜索…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}出現這個窗口後 然後再點這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顯示相貌、年齡和真實姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我下得不好還要讓你陪我下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果白子下這裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該這樣下吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下在這裏可以嗎? 或者下在這裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下哪裏都行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣行吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒? 就你們兩個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說去上網了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上網?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼好快啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天和進藤一起去看了一場職業圍棋公開賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他說一直坐著很沒意思 看到一半就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小光去幹什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是去上網了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道他怎麼會對上網感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有人在大廳裏介紹網上圍棋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就一直在聽那個人講解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到我看完職業比賽出來找他為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他去哪裏上網了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在三谷的姐姐打工的那家店裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐在網吧打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把地址告訴他之後 他就跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井學長 你來下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤崎你現在是不是懂點圍棋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 馬上就要放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋社怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要參加暑期輔導 有點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井學長已經是應試生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光從剛才的情形來看 可能會一直待在網吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想去那個圍棋會場轉轉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去小光之前去過的那個圍棋學校看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後下學期一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要招收幾個女社員 我也想參加大賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以去參加個人賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定要團體賽才行!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次看過你們比賽之後我就這麼覺得了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是團體賽更有意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們輸給了海王 但我還是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 團體賽的確很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的時候我們一星期見一次面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我也能來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:17.31,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&\move(227,361,227,215)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\fs20}{\bord0}網\N絡\N體\N驗\N空\N間\N\N配\N備\N最\N新\N系\N統
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界圍棋網? 是想進入這個網站嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然懂點電腦 對圍棋可是一竅不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 我學過圍棋的對局方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界圍棋網 搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入這裏我就可以和全世界的人下圍棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界? 你會英語嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會英語也沒關係 只是下棋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你昨天就一直看著這樣的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那個更扁些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 裏面的東西是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你到底要做什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你盡情地下你喜歡的圍棋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 剛才你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 三谷是怎麼學會下棋的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺還在世的時候教他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他上小學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個會下棋的老師 他們經常一起下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他畢業以後就去一些圍棋會場轉轉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑輝很厲害嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害啊 你不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊 那你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我? 我…普通水平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通水平就想在網上和全世界的人下棋?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 和實力高低又沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫你進入到這裏就可以了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我真的可以免費嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 不過要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不在的時候也不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候告訴我一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是 先起名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:34.81,gogo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA00000&}{\fnsimhei}{\pos(151,265)}{\fs30\be1}姓 名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:34.81,gogo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\pos(500,140)}{\fnsimhei\be1}入會申請表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 可以盡情地下? 真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字就叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我下個月要去日本待一個星期左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概有50個國家吧 一個國家派一個代表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在國內的預賽中拿了第一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦 還是亞洲最強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本 中國 還有韓國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國? 我們去年是第八名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過多虧了網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界圍棋的整體水平正在不斷提高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以找到很強的對手對局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽說日本現在的實力變弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 說著說著就又來了一個挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了 媽媽 注意身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai? 還是第一次看到這個名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我來看看你的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 和我下一局指導棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師正在為了下個月的國際業餘圍棋大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在網上進行特訓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來和你下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這種水平是做不了老師的練習對手的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師可是連續兩年代表荷蘭參賽了 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪算厲害啊 去年可是第六哦 第六名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今年可能會打破\N被亞洲選手獨佔鰲頭的局面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是老師的本職工作沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼沉迷於圍棋 還開辦了圍棋班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他可能會被開除 連教授的助手都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他是職業的 是職業棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在網上既不知道相貌也不知道名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說亞洲的職業棋手總是喜歡開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會裝成業餘選手在網上下棋消磨時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘敗 對手好強 差點讓我的心臟病發了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字從列表上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是第一次看到這個名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問了一下網友 誰也不知道他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai  究竟是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 暑假我們就來網上下棋讓你玩個夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 我每天都可以來下棋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 讓你下到膩為止 做好心理準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【GOGO】
